---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Project Flux Meridian — Technology Should Work for Everyone" description="We build free tools and provide free tech help. BRAIN is an open-source personal operating system for ADHD. FluxHelp is free tech support for anyone who needs it.">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero__content">
            <h1>Technology Should Work for Everyone</h1>
            <p class="hero__subtitle">We build free tools and provide free tech help — because access to technology shouldn't depend on who you are or what you can afford.</p>
            <a href="#pathways" class="btn btn--amber">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pathway Cards -->
    <section id="pathways" class="section pathways">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="sr-only">Our Work</h2>
            <div class="pathways__grid">
                <!-- FluxHelp — primary mission, goes first -->
                <a href="/fluxhelp" class="card">
                    <div class="card__icon card__icon--purple" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Need Help with Technology?</h3>
                    <p>Free tech help for anyone who needs it. No experience needed, no judgment — just real help from a real person.</p>
                    <span class="card__label" aria-hidden="true">Get Help &rarr;</span>
                </a>

                <!-- BRAIN -->
                <a href="https://github.com/WilliM233/brain3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card">
                    <div class="card__icon card__icon--amber" aria-hidden="true">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a8 8 0 0 0-8 8c0 3.4 2.1 6.3 5 7.4V20h6v-2.6c2.9-1.1 5-4 5-7.4a8 8 0 0 0-8-8z"/><path d="M12 2v4"/><path d="M8 22h8"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3>A Tool That Works with Your Brain</h3>
                    <p>A personal operating system built for ADHD. Open source, free forever for individuals.</p>
                    <span class="card__label" aria-hidden="true">Learn More &rarr;</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Story (Brief) -->
    <section class="section story">
        <div class="container story__content">
            <h2>Why Flux Meridian Exists</h2>
            <p>Flux Meridian started with one person who couldn't find tools that worked for their ADHD brain — so they built one. Along the way, they realized the community around them needed something too: safe, judgment-free tech help that actually met people where they were.</p>
            <p>Two arms of the same mission. BRAIN is a free, open-source tool that handles the executive function work so you can focus on doing. FluxHelp is free tech support for anyone who needs it — no experience required, no strings attached. Same philosophy behind both: meet people where they are.</p>
            <p>This isn't a startup pitch. It's a nonprofit mission. Technology should work for everyone, and we're building it that way.</p>
            <a href="/about" class="story__link">Read our full story &rarr;</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Get Involved -->
    <section class="section involved">
        <div class="container involved__content">
            <h2>Join the Mission</h2>
            <p>We're looking for testers for BRAIN, volunteers for FluxHelp, community partners, and people who want to spread the word. You don't need to be technical — you just need to care. Every bit helps.</p>
            <a href="mailto:support@fluxhelp.org" class="btn btn--amber">Get in Touch</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    /* Smooth scroll for anchor links */
    html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    /* ===== Hero ===== */
    .hero {
        min-height: 100dvh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-deep) 0%, var(--bg-mid) 100%);
    }

    .hero__content {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding-block: var(--space-3xl);
    }

    .hero__subtitle {
        font-size: var(--text-xl);
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        margin-top: var(--space-md);
        max-width: 600px;
    }

    .hero .btn {
        margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    }

    /* ===== Pathway Cards ===== */
    .pathways {
        background: var(--bg-mid);
    }

    .pathways__grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .card {
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
        border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
        padding: var(--space-xl);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: var(--space-md);
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform var(--transition-fast), border-color var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        border-color: var(--border-accent);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 24px var(--accent-glow);
    }

    .card:focus-visible {
        outline: 2px solid var(--accent-warm);
        outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .card h3 {
        font-size: var(--text-2xl);
        color: var(--text-primary);
    }

    .card p {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
        flex-grow: 1;
    }

    .card__label {
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        color: var(--accent-warm);
        margin-top: auto;
        transition: color var(--transition-fast);
    }

    .card:hover .card__label {
        color: var(--accent-warm-hover);
    }

    .card__icon {
        width: 56px;
        height: 56px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .card__icon--purple {
        background: var(--accent-glow);
        color: var(--accent-secondary);
    }

    .card__icon--amber {
        background: var(--accent-warm-glow);
        color: var(--accent-warm);
    }

    /* ===== Story ===== */
    .story__content {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .story__content h2 {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .story__content p {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .story__link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: var(--space-sm);
        font-family: var(--font-display);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ===== Get Involved ===== */
    .involved {
        background: var(--bg-mid);
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    }

    .involved__content {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 640px;
        margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .involved__content h2 {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    }

    .involved__content p {
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
        margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    }

    /* ===== Mobile ===== */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .pathways__grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .card {
            padding: var(--space-lg);
        }
    }
</style>
